headshotImage.caption: Mohammad Shahzad player page headshot cutout, 2021
headshotImage.longCaption: Mohammad Shahzad player page headshot cutout, 2021

commentTextItems.html: clips the ball down to long leg and that's the winning run! Ireland win by 6 wickets

commentPostTextItems.html: This result would have been hard to see when Ireland's third wicket fell with the score on 29. However a massive fourth wicket partnership of 144 between Ed Joyce and Kevin O'Brien really took the game away from Afghanistan. Once O'Brien went, Stirling came in and hit a quick fire 39 off 37 to keep Ed Joyce company on his march towards his century.

commentTextItems.html: drives the ball to the long-off boundary and the scores are tied
gets on the front foot and hits the ball past the cover fielder, he was always going to come back for his second to bring up the century
knocks the ball into the legside and Joyce gets to keep the strike
hits the ball through extra over again, this time he doesn't connect as well and they only get two
lovely shot from Stirling, its hit in the air through extra cover
driven back past the bowler to long-on
hits the ball in the air to the cover sweeper, bounces once before he fields it
hits the ball straight back past the bowler. It hits the stumps at the non-strikers end and they sneak the single
Joyce gets up on his toes and guides the ball to the right of backward point. Joyce is inching towards his century here.

headshotImage.caption: Rashid Khan player page headshot cutout, 2021
headshotImage.longCaption: Rashid Khan player page headshot cutout, 2021

commentTextItems.html: drops the ball into the off-side and Rashid comes in from extra cover to field
pulls the ball into the legside and Najibullah fields again
clips the ball into the legside and straight away Joyce says no, Just as well as the throw from Najibullah hits the non-strikers stumps
hits the ball in the air over the top of mid-on. One hand came off the bat as he hit it so it wasn't in total control
Stirling misses out on a full toss as he hits the ball back to the bowler
hits the ball back towards the bowler, it was in the air for a moment but lands safe

headshotImage.caption: Rashid Khan player page headshot cutout, 2021
headshotImage.longCaption: Rashid Khan player page headshot cutout, 2021

commentTextItems.html: turns the ball down to long leg, bit of confusion in the running so they only get a single
goes to cut the ball outside off-stump, misses and Shahzad can't gather it cleanly
gets in line and defends
gets onto the front foot and hits the ball up to long-off. Goes all the way along the ground

milestones.description: Mohammad Nabi and Rashid Khan's 53-run partnership is AFG's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 48 between Khaliq Dad and Mohammad Nabi
This is the highest match aggregate (473) involving teams Ireland & Afghanistan in ODIs
Shahzad has become the top scorer for AFG in ODIs with 1554 runs, going past Mohammad Nabi's 1488
Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (4) in ODIs for AFG, going past Nawroz Mangal's 4
Dawlat Zadran has become the top wicket-taker for AFG in ODIs with 62 wickets, going past Mohammad Nabi's 61
Rahmat Shah has taken the most five-wicket hauls (1) in ODIs for AFG, going past Hamid Hassan's record
